title: Lung Tumor_GT00006
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA and following clean-up with Qiagen Rneasy Mini Kit were performed according to the manufacturers instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 5 to 10 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix)
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip H133-A Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 400
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix Gene Chip Scanner.
data_processing: Gene expression data were processed and normalized using Bioconductor Affy package, based on the Robust Multichip Average (RMA) method5 for single-channel Affymetrix chips
